{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"categories":1,"event_categories":27},[2,9,15,21],{"id":3,"attributes":4},1,{"slug":5,"name":6,"description":7,"createdAt":8,"updatedAt":8},"nutrition","營養隨筆",null,"2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"id":10,"attributes":11},2,{"slug":12,"name":13,"description":7,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"reflection","感悟隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.692Z",{"id":16,"attributes":17},3,{"slug":18,"name":19,"description":7,"createdAt":20,"updatedAt":20},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-12T02:39:02.697Z",{"id":22,"attributes":23},4,{"slug":24,"name":25,"description":7,"createdAt":26,"updatedAt":26},"spiritual","心靈勵志","2023-02-12T02:39:02.698Z",[28,33,38,43,47,52],{"id":3,"attributes":29},{"name":30,"slug":31,"description":7,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"讀書會","book-sharing","2023-02-12T02:38:55.939Z",{"id":16,"attributes":34},{"name":35,"slug":36,"description":7,"createdAt":37,"updatedAt":37},"文化導賞","cultural","2023-02-12T02:38:55.943Z",{"id":22,"attributes":39},{"name":40,"slug":41,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"遊山玩水","hiking","2023-02-12T02:38:55.946Z",{"id":44,"attributes":45},5,{"name":46,"slug":18,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"健體運動",{"id":48,"attributes":49},6,{"name":50,"slug":5,"description":7,"createdAt":51,"updatedAt":51},"活學營養","2023-02-12T02:38:55.947Z",{"id":10,"attributes":53},{"name":54,"slug":55,"description":7,"createdAt":56,"updatedAt":57},"名人面對面","be-our-guest","2023-02-12T02:38:55.942Z","2023-03-08T13:16:12.875Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/categories?","http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/event-categories?"]},"slash":"always"},{"type":"data","data":[{"id":1,"attributes":2},169,{"title":3,"excerpt":4,"content":5,"slug":6,"createdAt":7,"updatedAt":7,"author":8,"categories":9,"tags":17,"image":33,"related_posts":34},"告別口罩瘡",null,"\n\n炎炎夏日，皮膚本身已較黐𥹉，而長時間戴口罩，所覆蓋皮膚的溫度上升，進一步刺激油脂分泌；加上呼出的空氣帶有水分，提高口罩內的濕度，令細菌更易滋生😖。\n\n皮膚本來就存在很多微生物如細菌，臉上的微生物及皮脂分泌「封在一起」，容易侵害皮膚，引致發炎，刺激粉刺、黑頭、暗瘡甚至痤瘡生長😭。若本來就容易長暗瘡，又或本身皮膚抵抗力較差，問題會更為嚴重。\n\n要加強皮膚的免疫力並修復皮膚，蛋白質極為重要💪🏻💪🏻。蛋白質更有助細胞鎖水，改善皮膚水油平衡。建議可多攝取植物性蛋白質☘️，包括豆類及堅果類，🥛奶類飲品也可選擇植物性的，例如豆奶、杏仁奶及燕麥奶。\n\n大豆和堅果同時含豐富卵磷脂，可促進皮膚新陳代謝，排除皮膚表面的毒素，減少粉刺、黑頭、暗瘡的形成，並有助去斑，亦有助皮膚水油平衡👍🏻🤗。\n\n此外，奧米加三脂肪酸Omega-3可減少身體發炎和㾗癢，提升免疫力，滋潤皮膚。Omega-3無法自行合成，必須從飲食攝取。香港人喜歡吃的三文魚、鯖魚和沙甸魚均含豐富Omega-3，惟必須注意所來自海域有否受重金屬污染，否則得不償失。","post200515","2020-05-15T00:00:00.000Z",{"data":4},{"data":10},[11],{"id":12,"attributes":13},1,{"slug":14,"name":15,"description":4,"createdAt":16,"updatedAt":16},"nutrition","營養隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"data":18},[19,24,28],{"id":20,"attributes":21},144,{"name":22,"createdAt":23,"updatedAt":23},"蛋白質","2023-02-12T03:32:01.351Z",{"id":1,"attributes":25},{"name":26,"createdAt":27,"updatedAt":27},"奧米加三","2023-02-12T03:32:01.366Z",{"id":29,"attributes":30},178,{"name":31,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"皮膚","2023-02-12T03:32:01.371Z",{"data":4},{"data":35},[]],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/posts?populate[author]=true&populate[categories]=true&populate[tags]=true&populate[image]=true&populate[related_posts]=true&filters[slug][$eq]=post200515"],"params":["slug"]}}]}